SQL_STMT_U.val:
select cast (sum (Payment_settlement) as decimal (13,2)) from
( select sum (CMON_CURRBALPAYMENTSETTLE) as Payment_settlement
from :1/clnt left join
:1/cmon on CMON_ADMNO = CLNT101_admno and CMON_CLNTNO = CLNT102_CLNTNO and
CMON_YEAR = :2 and
CMON_MONTH= :3 and
CMON_CURRENCY=':4'
where
CLNT103_COMM_ADMNO = :5 and
CLNT103_COMM_CLNTNO = :6
union
select sum (ACCC_MUTAPAYMENTSETTLE) as Payment_settlement
from :1/clnt left join
:1/accc on ACCC_ACCT_ADMNO = CLNT101_admno and ACCC_ACCT_CLNTNO= CLNT102_CLNTNO and
(ACCC_MUTTYPE = 98 or ACCC_MUTTYPE=99)
where
CLNT103_COMM_ADMNO = :5 and
CLNT103_COMM_CLNTNO = :6 )sq
